            style={{
              marginTop: '12px',
              color: colors.textSecondary,
              fontSize: '14px',
              lineHeight: '1.6',
              maxWidth: '300px',
            }}
          >
            A reimagined MMORPG ecosystem. Enter the Perfect World and forge your legend.
